verse osmosis membrane module requires chemical cleaning. Note: If necessary, the proposed model can be equipped with a dosing pump antiskalanta; controller with indication of the electrical conductivity of demineralized water. Consumables: Antiskalant, polypropylene cartridges are mechanical filter.', '', 'E-MO6000LPD MINI Compact');
